    euai:chunkText ", Article 9(1) of Regulation (EU) 2016/679 and Article 10(1) of Regulation (EU) 2018/1725 prohibit the  processing of biometric data subject to limited exceptions as provided in those Articles. In the application of Article  9(1) of Regulation (EU) 2016/679, the use of remote biometric identification for purposes other than law  enforcement has already been subject to prohibition decisions by national data protection authorities. (40) In accordance with Article" ;
