    euai:chunkText "intention to distort behaviour where the distortion results from factors external to the AI system which are outside  the control of the provider or the deployer, namely factors that may not be reasonably foreseeable and therefore not  possible for the provider or the deployer of the AI system to mitigate. In any case, it is not necessary for the provider  or the deployer to have the intention to cause significant harm, provided that such harm results from the  manipulative or exploitative AI-enabled practices. The prohibitions" ;
