    euai:chunkText " does not necessarily reveal substantial  information on the data set used for the training or fine-tuning of the model and on how compliance of copyright  law was thereby ensured, the exception provided for general-purpose AI models from compliance with the  transparency-related requirements should not concern the obligation to produce a summary about the content used  for model training and the obligation to put in place a policy to comply with Union copyright law, in particular to  identify and comply with the reservation of rights pursuant to" ;
