    euai:chunkText "  through either Union or national law directly related to public safety or security or through the clear manifestation  OJ L, 12.7.2024 EN ELI: http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg/2024/1689/oj 5/144" ;
    euai:contentOffset 33784 ;
