    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText " protection, against  the harmful effects of AI systems in the Union and supporting innovation. 2. This Regulation lays down: (a) harmonised rules for the placing on the market, the putting into service, and the use of AI systems in the Union; EN OJ L, 12.7.2024 44/144 ELI: http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg/2024/1689/oj" ;
