    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText " other regulations. Therefore,  proportionate transparency measures should be laid down, including the drawing up and keeping up to date of  documentation, and the provision of information on the general-purpose AI model for its usage by the downstream  providers. Technical documentation should be prepared and kept up to date by the general-purpose AI model  provider for the purpose of making it available, upon request, to the AI Office and the national competent  authorities. The minimal set of elements to be included in such" ;
    euai:contentOffset 183398 ;
