    euai:chunkText "data.europa.eu/eli/reg/2024/1689/oj (18) Council Framework Decision 2002/584/JHA of 13 June 2002 on the European arrest warrant and the surrender procedures  between Member States (OJ L 190, 18.7.2002, p. 1). (19) Directive (EU) 2022/2557 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 14 December 2022 on the resilience of critical entities  and repealing Council Directive 2008/114" ;
