    euai:chunkText " an annex to this Regulation is based on the 32 criminal  offences listed in the Council Framework Decision 2002/584/JHA (18), taking into account that some of those  offences are, in practice, likely to be more relevant than others, in that the recourse to ‘real-time’ remote biometric  identification could, foreseeably, be necessary and proportionate to highly varying degrees for the practical pursuit  of the localisation or identification of a perpetrator or suspect of the different" ;
