euai_c:b2f0aea760c180a174396001c50cfeeb520202cf a euai:DocumentChunk ;
    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText " of  AI systems in the context of the use of lethal force and other AI systems in the context of military and defence  activities. As regards national security purposes, the exclusion is justified both by the fact that national security  remains the sole responsibility of Member States in accordance with Article 4(2) TEU and by the specific nature and  operational needs of national security activities and specific national rules applicable to those activities. Nonetheless,  if an AI system developed, placed on the market, put into" ;
    euai:contentOffset 42647 ;
    euai:fileName "EUAIAct-1-44.pdf" ;
    euai:pageNumber 7 ;
    euai:position 90 .

