    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText " in this Regulation should be interpreted in light of the notion of biometric data  as defined in Article 4, point (14) of Regulation (EU) 2016/679, Article 3, point (18) of Regulation (EU) 2018/1725  and Article 3, point (13) of Directive (EU) 2016/680. Biometric data can allow for the authentication, identification  or categorisation of natural persons and for the recognition of emotions of natural persons. (15) The" ;
