    euai:chunkText " of that standard, this should  OJ L, 12.7.2024 EN ELI: http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg/2024/1689/oj 31/144 (41) Regulation (EU) No 1025/2012 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 25 October 2012 on European standardisation,  amending Council Directives 89/686/EEC and 93/15/EEC and Directives 94/9/EC" ;
