    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText " AI systems referred to in pre-defined areas  specified in this Regulation do not lead to a significant risk of harm to the legal interests protected under those areas  because they do not materially influence the decision-making or do not harm those interests substantially. For the  purposes of this Regulation, an AI system that does not materially influence the outcome of decision-making should  be understood to be an AI system that does not have an impact on the substance, and thereby the outcome, of  decision-" ;
