    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText " materially distorting the behaviour of a person and in a manner that causes or is  reasonably likely to cause significant harm to that or another person or groups of persons, including harms that may  be accumulated over time and should therefore be prohibited. It may not be possible to assume that there is an  EN OJ L, 12.7.2024 8/144 ELI: http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg/2024/1689/oj (16)" ;
    euai:contentOffset 54802 ;
