    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText "inal components such as  audio, image, video stimuli that persons cannot perceive, as those stimuli are beyond human perception, or other  manipulative or deceptive techniques that subvert or impair person’s autonomy, decision-making or free choice in  ways that people are not consciously aware of those techniques or, where they are aware of them, can still be  deceived or are not able to control or resist them. This could be facilitated, for example, by machine-brain interfaces  or virtual" ;
    euai:contentOffset 53286 ;
    euai:fileName "EUAIAct-1-44.pdf" ;
