    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText " has already been subject to prohibition decisions by national data protection authorities. (40) In accordance with Article 6a of Protocol No 21 on the position of the United Kingdom and Ireland in respect of the  area of freedom, security and justice, as annexed to the TEU and to the TFEU, Ireland is not bound by the rules laid  down in Article 5(1), first subparagraph, point (g), to the extent it applies to the use of biometric categorisation  systems for" ;
