    euai:chunkText "(9) Harmonised rules applicable to the placing on the market, the putting into service and the use of high-risk AI  systems should be laid down consistently with Regulation (EC) No 765/2008 of the European Parliament and of the  Council (7), Decision No 768/2008/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council (8) and Regulation (EU)  2019/1020 of the European Parliament and of the Council (9) (New Legislative Framework). The" ;
