    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText " devices  and software. Post-market monitoring should not cover sensitive operational data of deployers which are law  enforcement authorities. This system is also key to ensure that the possible risks emerging from AI systems which  continue to ‘learn’ after being placed on the market or put into service can be more efficiently and timely addressed.  In this context, providers should also be required to have a system in place to report to the relevant authorities any  serious incidents resulting from the use of their AI" ;
