    euai:chunkText " machines. The reference  to explicit or implicit objectives underscores that AI systems can operate according to explicit defined objectives or  to implicit objectives. The objectives of the AI system may be different from the intended purpose of the AI system  in a specific context. For the purposes of this Regulation, environments should be understood to be the contexts in  which the AI systems operate, whereas outputs generated by the AI system reflect different functions performed by  AI systems and include predictions, content, recommendations or decisions. AI systems" ;
