    euai:chunkText " a whole due to its digital components, including AI systems, are duly prevented and mitigated. For instance,  increasingly autonomous robots, whether in the context of manufacturing or personal assistance and care should be  able to safely operate and performs their functions in complex environments. Similarly, in the health sector where  the stakes for life and health are particularly high, increasingly sophisticated diagnostics systems and systems  supporting human decisions should be reliable and accurate. (48) The extent of the adverse impact caused by the" ;
