    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText " the Union and the  Member States are legally obliged to protect persons with disabilities from discrimination and promote their equality,  to ensure that persons with disabilities have access, on an equal basis with others, to information and  communications technologies and systems, and to ensure respect for privacy for persons with disabilities. Given the  growing importance and use of AI systems, the application of universal design principles to all new technologies and  services should ensure full and equal access for everyone potentially affected by or using AI technologies, including" ;
