    euai:chunkText " information right is ancillary and necessary to the objective of  protecting fundamental rights that underlies this Regulation. Therefore, an information requirement to that effect  should be laid down in this Regulation, without affecting any existing rights of workers. (93) Whilst risks related to AI systems can result from the way such systems are designed, risks can as well stem from  how such AI systems are used. Deployers of high-risk AI system therefore play a critical role in ensuring that  fundamental rights are" ;
