    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText "risk AI systems, since they may determine  the educational and professional course of a person’s life and therefore may affect that person’s ability to secure  a livelihood. When improperly designed and used, such systems may be particularly intrusive and may violate the  right to education and training as well as the right not to be discriminated against and perpetuate historical patterns  of discrimination, for example against women, certain age groups, persons with disabilities, or persons of certain  racial or ethnic origins or" ;
