    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText " or resist them. This could be facilitated, for example, by machine-brain interfaces  or virtual reality as they allow for a higher degree of control of what stimuli are presented to persons, insofar as they  may materially distort their behaviour in a significantly harmful manner. In addition, AI systems may also otherwise  exploit the vulnerabilities of a person or a specific group of persons due to their age, disability within the meaning of  Directive (EU) 2019/882 of the European Parliament and of the Council" ;
