    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText " effectively reversed and  disregarded and that personal data is protected and is deleted when the subjects have withdrawn their consent to  participate in the testing without prejudice to their rights as data subjects under the Union data protection law. As  regards transfer of data, it is also appropriate to envisage that data collected and processed for the purpose of testing  in real-world conditions should be transferred to third countries only where appropriate and applicable safeguards  under Union law are implemented, in particular in accordance with bases for transfer" ;
    euai:contentOffset 248818 ;
    euai:fileName "EUAIAct-1-44.pdf" ;
