    euai:chunkOf <https://euaiact.eu/resource/Document/EUAIAct-1-44_pdf> ;
    euai:chunkText " a model could, inter alia, also be determined by a number of parameters, models with at  least a billion of parameters and trained with a large amount of data using self-supervision at scale should be  considered to display significant generality and to competently perform a wide range of distinctive tasks. (99) Large generative AI models are a typical example for a general-purpose AI model, given that they allow for flexible  generation of content, such as in the form of text" ;
    euai:contentOffset 181675 ;
    euai:fileName "EUAIAct-1-44.pdf" ;
