    euai:chunkText "ers if they want to carry out text and  data mining over such works. (106) Providers that place general-purpose AI models on the Union market should ensure compliance with the relevant  obligations in this Regulation. To that end, providers of general-purpose AI models should put in place a policy to  comply with Union law on copyright and related rights, in particular to identify and comply with the reservation of  rights expressed by rightsholders pursuant to Article 4(3) of Directive" ;
