    euai:chunkText " in this  Regulation for models should continue to apply in addition to those for AI systems. The obligations laid down for  models should in any case not apply when an own model is used for purely internal processes that are not essential  for providing a product or a service to third parties and the rights of natural persons are not affected. Considering  their potential significantly negative effects, the general-purpose AI models with systemic risk should always be  subject to the relevant obligations under this Regulation. The definition should not" ;
