    euai:chunkText " resembles existing persons, objects, places,  entities or events and would falsely appear to a person to be authentic or truthful (deep fakes), should also clearly  and distinguishably disclose that the content has been artificially created or manipulated by labelling the AI output  accordingly and disclosing its artificial origin. Compliance with this transparency obligation should not be  interpreted as indicating that the use of the AI system or its output impedes the right to freedom of expression and  the right to freedom of the arts and" ;
