    euai:chunkText " behalf  to assist judicial authorities in researching and interpreting facts and the law and in applying the law to a concrete set  of facts. AI systems intended to be used by alternative dispute resolution bodies for those purposes should also be  considered to be high-risk when the outcomes of the alternative dispute resolution proceedings produce legal effects  for the parties. The use of AI tools can support the decision-making power of judges or judicial independence, but  should not replace it: the final decision-making must remain" ;
